{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":127,"Text":"他們否認他，所以他們必定要被拘禁。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":128,"Text":"惟真主的純潔的眾僕則不然。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":129,"Text":"我使他的令名，永存於後代。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":130,"Text":"「祝易勒雅斯平安！」"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":131,"Text":"我必定要這樣報酬行善者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":132,"Text":"他確是我的信道的僕人。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":133,"Text":"魯特確是使者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":134,"Text":"當時，我拯救了他，和他的全體信徒；"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":135,"Text":"惟有一個老婦人和其餘的人，沒有獲得拯救。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":136,"Text":"然後，我毀滅了別的許多人。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":137,"Text":"你們的確朝夕經過他們的遺蹟，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":138,"Text":"難道你們不了解嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":139,"Text":"優努司確是使者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":140,"Text":"當時，他逃到那只滿載的船舶上。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":141,"Text":"他就拈【門龜】，他卻是失敗的，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":142,"Text":"大魚就吞了他，同時，他是應受譴責的。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":143,"Text":"假若他不是常讚頌真主者，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":144,"Text":"他必葬身魚腹，直到世人復活之日。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":145,"Text":"然後，我將他拋在旱地上，當時他是有病的。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":146,"Text":"我使一棵瓠瓜，長起來遮著他。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":147,"Text":"我曾派遣他去教化十多萬民眾。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":148,"Text":"他們便歸信他，我使他們享樂至一定期。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":149,"Text":"你問他們吧！你的主有許多女兒，他們卻有多少兒子呢？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":150,"Text":"還是我曾將眾天神造成女性的，他們曾眼見我的創造呢？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":151,"Text":"真的，他們因為自己的悖謬，必定要說："},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":152,"Text":"「真主已生育了。」他們確是說謊者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":153,"Text":"難道他不要兒子，卻要女兒嗎？"}]}